name: The Cars: Live

review.name: One of my favorite bands! See why
review.reviewBody: 6/2/18. More like 3 1/2 stars. It was great to see one of my favorite groups playing their early hits in an intimate setting instead of a big gigantic stadium. Haven't heard them in so long, it was great to see just how good they really were. I enjoyed the interview that was included on the DVD,in which the viewer had the last chance to see Benjamin Orr before he died a few months after the interview. He looked awful (pancreatic cancer), but it was good to hear what he had to say. If you are a Cars fan, then you need to watch this!
